name: Youngr - Run La Peregrina Live From Llamaland Studios

metadata.name: Youngr - Run (La Peregrina) (Live From Llamaland Studios)
metadata.description:
Run (La Peregrina) is my third video NFT release on Glass.xyz! 😎

This is one of the first songs I ever wrote and after 7 years I'm finally  releasing it! I'm especially excited as I'm releasing the video as an NFT as I get deeper into the web3 space.  

I'll be minting all summer and I'm so honoured that each video has sold out so far, thank you to the web3 community for embracing my music and videos and thank you to glass.xyz for backing me!

More to come 🏃🏾‍♂️🏃🏾‍♂️🏃🏾‍♂️
